output.sentences: There is an Easter egg hunt for all ages.
The kids all stand around, waiting for the eggs to appear.
The eggs appear and all of the kids are stepping on them.
Unfortunately, the eggs are cursed, causing rapid aging.
Some of the kids are now adults, but others have morphed into donkeys.
